## Understanding the System

### Core Concepts

**Profile**: A folder containing game-specific settings, controller mappings, and configurations.

**Launcher**: An executable that loads a profile and launches your game with all configured tools.

**Plugin**: A module that integrates external tools (controller mappers, cloud backup, etc.).

**Sequence**: The order in which tools are executed before and after your game runs.

