## Advanced Workflows

### Multi-PC Gaming Setup

Sync saves across desktop and laptop:

```ini
RcloneSyncMode=sync
RcloneBackupOnLaunch=True
RcloneBackupOnExit=True
```

### Streaming Setup

Optimized for streaming:

```ini
MultiMonitorGamingConfig=Profiles\streaming.cfg
Player1Profile=Profiles\Streaming_Controls.amgp
```

### Competitive Gaming

Maximum performance:

```ini
[Sequences]
LaunchSequence=Monitor-Config,Controller-Mapper
# Skip cloud sync for minimal latency
```

